#X text 119 62 Unlike [lop~] from Vanilla or [else/lop2~] \, this filter has a zero fixed at -1 on the z-plane \, which means Nyquist is always filtered out. Nonetheless \, if you reach nyquist \, the fiter bypasses. Hence \, as you reach nyquist \, it is like the filter has no action and the output is the same as the input., f 43;
